{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">NOTIFICACION</div><br><br></div>", "i": 6349367}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Mediante resoluci&#xF3;n n&#xFA;mero 116, de fecha 9 de agosto de 2001, el Serviu IV Regi&#xF3;n se desisti&#xF3; de la expropiaci&#xF3;n de 13 lotes del sector de Caleta Hornos, comuna de La Higuera, provincia de Elqui, IV Regi&#xF3;n, expropiaci&#xF3;n dispuesta en virtud de lo estipulado por la ley N&#xBA; 16.391 y D.L. 2.186/78, Minvu.</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  La individualizaci&#xF3;n de esos 13 lotes aparece en el plano de expropiaci&#xF3;n de Caleta Hornos y los datos m&#xE1;s relevantes de cada uno de ellos, son los siguientes:</div><br><div class=\"p\">Lote&nbsp; &nbsp; Rol de Aval&#xFA;o&nbsp; &nbsp;  Presunto&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Superficie Mt2</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Propietario</div><br><div class=\"p\">R1&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  28-001&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Sucesi&#xF3;n Flores&nbsp; &nbsp;  40.115,9</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Villalobos</div><div class=\"p\">R2&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  28-001&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  23.595,8</div><div class=\"p\">R3&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  28-001&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 9.476</div><div class=\"p\">R4&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  28-001&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1.656,2</div><div class=\"p\">R5&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  28-001&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 6.161,5</div><div class=\"p\">U1&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  28-001&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3.984,7</div><d